@startuml 高频数据采集与分发系统V2.0_架构图
!theme plain

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam packageFontSize 13
skinparam packageFontStyle bold
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei

' ===== 图例 =====
legend right
  |= 颜色 |= 层级 |
  |<#E8F5E9>| 数据采集与结构化层 |
  |<#FFF3E0>| 核心数据总线层 |
  |<#E3F2FD>| 数据持久化层 |
  |<#F3E5F5>| 数据分发层 |
  |<#FFEBEE>| 数据检测与工况判别层 |
  |<#FFFDE7>| MMF/共享内存 |
  |<#E0F2F1>| MQTT 发布 |
endlegend

title **高频数据采集与分发系统 V2.0 — 架构总览**

' =====================================================
' 1. 子进程 (ConsoleApp1)
' =====================================================
package "子进程 ConsoleApp1 (数据采集与预处理)" as ChildProcess #E8EAF6 {

  ' 1.1 4个内部线程
  rectangle ADWork as "ADWork\n(数据采集线程)" #E8F5E9
  rectangle ADDraw as "ADDraw\n(数据预处理线程)" #E8F5E9
  rectangle Analysis as "Analysis\n(结构化分析线程)" #E8F5E9
  rectangle UIThread as "UI刷新线程" #F3E5F5

  rectangle Detection as "数据检测分析线程" #FFEBEE
  rectangle Persist as "数据持久化线程" #E3F2FD

  ' 内部 Channel 数据流
  ADWork -right-> ADDraw : Channel<Data_Block>\n原始二进制数据
  ADDraw -right-> Analysis : Channel<Voltage_block>\n电压值
  ADDraw --> UIThread : 直读原始电压值\n(文档关键设计)
}

' =====================================================
' 2. 数据总线层 (MMF)
' =====================================================
rectangle "核心数据总线\nRawRingBuffer (环形缓冲区+MMF)\n单写多读·写指针前一段" as RawBus #FFF3E0

rectangle "UI专用缓冲区\nUISharedBuffer (独立MMF)\n隔离·BufferLength>PixelCount" as UIBuffer #FFFDE7

' 数据流向: Analysis → 核心总线
Analysis -down-> RawBus : 结构化数据写入\n(CH1/CH2/Vis/Cn2)

' 数据流向: 核心总线 → 各读取端
RawBus -down-> Detection : "读取写指针前一段\n(高频实时检测)"
RawBus -right-> Persist : "周期读取\n(1s/5s/30s/1min)"
RawBus --> [低频UI分发] : "7s周期\n(低频数据)"

' 数据流向: UI线程 → UI专用缓冲区
UIThread -down-> UIBuffer : "降采样1000:1\nWriteSampleBatch()"

' =====================================================
' 3. 主进程 (WebAPI)
' =====================================================
package "主进程 WebAPI (托管+发布)" as MainProcess #F1F8E9 {

  rectangle WaveformPub as "WaveformPublishService\n(主控进程)" #F1F8E9
  rectangle MqttRpc as "MQTT RPC 主通道服务\nCollector/Laser/System/Log" #F1F8E9
  rectangle WebSocket as "WebSocket / SignalR\n实时推送" #F1F8E9
}

' 主进程从UI专用缓冲区读取
UIBuffer -down-> WaveformPub : ReadLatestFrame()\n33ms周期

' =====================================================
' 4. MQTT 服务器
' =====================================================
rectangle "MQTT 服务器\n(EMQX / Mosquitto)" as MqttBroker #E0F2F1

rectangle "低频Topic" as LowTopic #E0F2F1
rectangle "实时Topic" as RealTopic #E0F2F1
rectangle "告警Topic" as AlarmTopic #E0F2F1

MqttBroker --> LowTopic
MqttBroker --> RealTopic
MqttBroker --> AlarmTopic

' MQTT 发布连接
WaveformPub -right-> RealTopic : 实时波形数据
[低频UI分发] -right-> LowTopic : 低频统计数据
Detection -right-> AlarmTopic : 异常告警事件

' =====================================================
' 5. 前端
' =====================================================
rectangle "前端 Web 界面\n趋势图表·波形渲染·告警弹窗" as Frontend #FBE9E7

LowTopic -down-> Frontend : 订阅
RealTopic -down-> Frontend : 订阅
AlarmTopic -down-> Frontend : 订阅
WebSocket -right-> Frontend : WebSocket直连

' =====================================================
' 6. 外部硬件
' =====================================================
rectangle "采集硬件\n(1MHz 采样卡)" as Hardware #FFCCBC
Hardware -down-> ADWork : 原始二进制数据

' ===== 设计要点标注 =====
note bottom of RawBus
  **核心数据总线关键设计:**
  1. 单写多读, 无需加锁
  2. 所有读取端读"写指针前一段"
  3. 写指针永远领先读指针
  4. 缓冲区大小适配 1MHz 采集率
end note

note right of UIBuffer
  **UI专用缓冲区隔离设计:**
  1. 与核心总线物理隔离
  2. 仅服务高频实时链路
  3. 降采样比 1000:1
  4. 主控进程唯一数据源
end note

@enduml
